<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Music on Compossible</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/categories/music/</link><description>Recent content in Music on Compossible</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-GB</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 11:51:41 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/categories/music/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Solipsism at St Peter’s</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/11/16/solipsism-at-st-peters/</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Nov 2025 17:04:53 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/11/16/solipsism-at-st-peters/</guid><description>&lt;p>I tried to &lt;em>sklent&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>to see if you&lt;/p>
&lt;p>were enjoying Joep&lt;/p>
&lt;p>as much as I&lt;/p>
&lt;p>the Dutch poet&lt;/p>
&lt;p>at the pulpit&lt;/p>
&lt;p>(in his sanctuary)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>striking looking&lt;/p>
&lt;p>like an&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Old Testament&lt;/p>
&lt;p>prophet&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>I heard the keys&lt;/p>
&lt;p>gentle Goliath&lt;/p>
&lt;p>struck&lt;/p>
&lt;p>to unlock&lt;/p>
&lt;p>the magic wooden box&lt;/p>
&lt;p>and the sounds drifted up&lt;/p>
&lt;p>t&amp;rsquo;wards heaven&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Between Man &amp; Machine</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/09/18/between-man-machine/</link><pubDate>Thu, 18 Sep 2025 12:47:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/09/18/between-man-machine/</guid><description>&lt;p>Music made using my poems&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I have been experimenting again using AI to make songs from my poems. This is the first full &amp;lsquo;album&amp;rsquo;, the sound quality is not studio quality (and requires mastering) but it is an interesting experiment!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.bandlab.com/poetones/albums/67e79540-b387-f011-b482-000d3a97c7d6">&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/between-man-machine-cover-1.webp" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.bandlab.com/poetones/albums/67e79540-b387-f011-b482-000d3a97c7d6">Bandlab&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.bandlab.com/poetones/albums/67e79540-b387-f011-b482-000d3a97c7d6">&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/thepinkpanther._reflect_refract_the_undying_light_van_gogh_styl_1d57bfac-3c2c-4f79-9ee4-d6bfea317fbe-gigapixel-high-fidelity-v2-1.5x-edit-2.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>AI generated&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>We Are Dawn</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/09/11/we-are-dawn/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Sep 2025 18:55:48 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/09/11/we-are-dawn/</guid><description>&lt;p>Poem and AI song &amp;amp; video&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Audio version (my voice)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">View this post on Instagram&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">A post shared by Peter Pink-Howitt (@peterhowitt)&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>We Are Dawn&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Shy moon&lt;br>
Hiding with&lt;br>
Dwining stars&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/shy-moon.webp" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Slow sun&lt;br>
Sauntering o’er&lt;br>
Weald and tor&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/sun.png" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Green land&lt;br>
Breathing loam&lt;br>
Seeding sky&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>The Silence Inside</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/08/28/the-silence-inside/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Aug 2025 12:54:22 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/08/28/the-silence-inside/</guid><description>&lt;p>Experimental AI album&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I also tried my hand at an AI generated album &amp;lsquo;&lt;a href="https://www.bandlab.com/poetones/albums/7688ead4-e183-f011-b482-000d3a97c7d6">The Silence Inside&lt;/a>&amp;rsquo;: a mixture of some of my poetry and instrumental music all using similar prompts to give the whole thing a (hopefully) coherent sound. Unfortunately AI can not yet produce studio quality tracks.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Listen With or Without Prejudice&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>